data.description: A touch of New England charm in Ulster County! Come and view this lovely Saltbox style home located on 1.6 acres in the Wallkill School District. A magnificent fieldstone fireplace in the living room is a delightful centerpiece. Beautiful hardwood flooring. Offering 3/4 bedrooms with the option of a 1st floor bedroom or a home office/den. Large 2nd floor bedrooms to include a primary suite and 2 additional bedrooms and full bathroom. Kitchen/dining room combo is great for entreating. An Extra Large laundry room could even host a small office space. Enjoy the outdoor space with a patio area, wide open field with a run in shed. Bring your imagination it can be fulfilled here!
